The theme which I have chosen,

00:00:05.445 --> 00:00:09.165
along with many others, supports add-in widgets.

00:00:09.165 --> 00:00:12.240
A widget is a small feature or

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:16.515
a small piece of content which we can place into our theme.

00:00:16.515 --> 00:00:21.570
Now, we can't just go ahead and place these widgets into any area which we would like.

00:00:21.570 --> 00:00:27.750
These widget areas where we can drop these into has been preset by the themes offer.

00:00:27.750 --> 00:00:32.970
Let's take a look at how we can work with widgets with our current theme.

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:38.255
If we go back over to our homepage and into the edit section,

00:00:38.255 --> 00:00:43.100
right down at the very bottom below all of our blocks with the under the layout section,

00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:44.915
we have these footer widgets.

00:00:44.915 --> 00:00:47.300
The author of this theme has allowed us to assess

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:50.725
how many areas we want to customize inside the footer.

00:00:50.725 --> 00:00:53.300
The default value is free,

00:00:53.300 --> 00:00:58.250
meaning the footer is split into three sections where we can add our content blocks.

00:00:58.250 --> 00:01:00.410
Also, remember from just above this,

00:01:00.410 --> 00:01:01.955
we have this sidebar section,

00:01:01.955 --> 00:01:05.165
where we can lay out our content alongside a sidebar.

00:01:05.165 --> 00:01:11.230
Well, both the sidebars section and also the footer section and both exact widget.

00:01:11.230 --> 00:01:13.070
To access our widgets,

00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:15.890
we go back to the main dashboard and then into

00:01:15.890 --> 00:01:19.765
the appearance section where we have a dedicated widgets menu.

00:01:19.765 --> 00:01:23.150
This page has been split into two sections,

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:24.320
where on the left we have

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:28.400
the available widgets which we can add to our project such as calendars,

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:32.540
menus, search boxes, and also things related to our blog,

00:01:32.540 --> 00:01:34.975
so just comments and recent posts.

00:01:34.975 --> 00:01:36.620
