00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:40.625
the available theme areas where we can add these widgets too,

00:01:40.625 --> 00:01:42.710
all these sections can be customized,

00:01:42.710 --> 00:01:45.625
and I'm now going to add some widgets into the footer.

